column4: Anyone using Eclipse on Ubuntu?  More specifically, PHPeclipse?
I am using it in Gentoo, but ask anyhow, see if I can help.
I'm having issues getting autocomplete and debugging working.  The PHPeclipse plugin won't let me add an interpreter and everything I find on the web is centered around doing it with Windows
Hmm, interpreters, that is explainable, but the autocomplete is really weird...
